1.title: Save the Town

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

1.plot: After blocking the way to the Netherworld, Puss and company return to San Lorenzo to find a town that's greatly changed -- with a new man in charge!

2.title: Save the Cat

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

2.plot: Puss rallies the San Lorenzans to save their town before El Moco blows it to bits. But building an army requires Puss to swallow his pride.

3.title: Lost and Foundlings

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

3.plot: The orphans compete in a high-stakes contest at the Duchess's command. A strange rumbling shakes things up in San Lorenzo.

4.title: The Scarlet Panther

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

4.plot: A notorious loan shark shows up in San Lorenzo and insists that Puss's boots belong to him. But without them, Puss just isn't the same.

5.title: Pajuna Serves Spirits

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

5.plot: It began as a harmless parlor trick. But when Pajuna summons ghosts from the other side, vengeful spirits start taking over the townsfolk.

6.title: One Last Jobs

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

6.plot: Assuming it'll be easy, Puss offers to run the Cow and Moone for Pajuna while she's off on an adventure with her old pal, Roz.

7.title: Like a Fox

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

7.plot: A handsome face stirs up jealousy when famed treasure hunter Guy Fox asks a star-struck Dulcinea to join him on his next adventure.

8.title: Not a Date

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

8.plot: Puss and Dulcinea decide to go on a vacation together, though neither of them will admit it's a date. Especially when the whole town comes along.

9.title: Flock the Boat

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

9.plot: The townsfolk look to Puss to stop San Lorenzo's earthquakes. But first, a mission to rescue a pirate captain from the island of Doom.

10.title: All Hail, Puss!

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

10.plot: When the sky gods grant Puss devine powers to calm the earthquakes, his oversized ego threatens to turn the whole town against him.

11.title: The Moving Finger Writes

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

11.plot: With the future of the world at stake, Puss and his friends head to the Forbidden Citadel on a mission to find the Great Mage Sino.

12.title: And, Having Writ, Moves On

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

12.plot: The Great Mage Sino reveals the full history of San Lorenzo and the only way to save it, which requires Puss to give up everything.

1.title: Hidden

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

1.plot: Puss stumbles upon the legendary hidden city of San Lorenzo, and soon finds himself forced to protect it from thieves.

2.title: Sphinx

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

2.plot: Puss accidentally gives the orphans a magic substance that will ultimately make them explode. The only cure is guarded by a Sphinx who challenges Puss with riddles - and contrary to his own belief, Puss is not good at riddles.

3.title: Brothers

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

3.plot: Puss is Toby's new BFFAEAE and it's driving Puss crazy, but when Toby is kidnapped by his ninja brothers, Puss realizes how much he misses the big oaf. Unfortunately, the brothers use Toby to steal a powerful gauntlet from the treasure house, which they plan to use for "mad evil, bro."

4.title: Duchess

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

4.plot: The Duchess seeks Artephius' soul for her spell collection, and it's up to Puss to protect him. It turns out that The Duchess and Artephius have a complicated relationship.

5.title: Adventure

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

5.plot: Puss misses the old days adventuring with his buddy Jack Sprat. Fearful he will leave San Lorenzo, Dulcinea concocts a super special adventure surprise with the orphans. But Jack Sprat shows up with the promise of a damsel in distress... who turns out to be a super scary monster.

6.title: Fountains

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

6.plot: Puss's old mentor, El Guante Blanco, stumbles into town and seeks help from his pupil. Puss, Dulcinea, and El Guante start on a journey to find the fountain of youth.

7.title: Bravery

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

7.plot: Puss puts on a skit to make the Mayor feel more confident. However, the concept of being completely "fearless" goes to the Mayor's head, and he starts doing reckless things.

8.title: Golem

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

8.plot: The Golem, a giant clay enemy Puss has been outrunning for years, comes to San Lorenzo. With the help of Artephius, Puss may finally defeat his foe.

9.title: Boots

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

9.plot: By stealing enchanted boots from the Treasure House, Jack Sprat sets off a dangerous Devil Wind that threatens to consume all of the town's treasure.

10.title: Sword

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

10.plot: Dulcinea becomes enchanted with heroic powers when she pulls a magical sword from a stone, and Puss must help her learn how to control her strength.

11.title: Mouse

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

11.plot: Puss is obsessed with catching an adorable mouse, but when strange things happen in town, he fears the rodent may be more than a delicious meal.

12.title: Goblin

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

12.plot: When a young goblin arrives in town, Puss tries to convince the orphans that she is more than just a scaly troublemaker.

13.title: Star

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

13.plot: Dulcinea secretly discovers a wishing star and while trying to make things better through wishes, actually makes things a lot worse.

14.title: Pigs

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

14.plot: Toby's dim-bulb of a brother, Brandt, returns to San Lorenzo and begs Puss to help him reunite with his band of ninja brothers.

15.title: Luck

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

15.plot: Puss learns that black is the new orange when a curse transforms him into an unlucky black cat. Cast out of town he must learn how to break the spell.

1.title: Dragon

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

1.plot: Puss promises to kill a dragon that is scaring towns close by. But when he meets it face to face, he changes his plans.

2.title: Moles

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

2.plot: While Puss and his best friend, Jack Sprat, look for treasure underground, they find an odd kingdom.

3.title: Mermaid

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

3.plot: To prove he is a ladies' hero, Puss saves a mermaid from a thief who quickly falls in love with him - and becomes a big problem.

4.title: Bees

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

4.plot: Puss gets scared when angry bees invade the town, so he calls on the Piper, who has helpful powers.

5.title: Squad

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

5.plot: While Puss trains the orphans to work as a team to protect San Lorenzo, a villain comes to town and kidnaps him.

6.title: Spells

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

7.title: Scimitar

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

7.plot: While Puss looks for items missing from the treasure house, he gets help from the Scimitar, an evil sword.

8.title: Stories

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

8.plot: An angry thunder god demands to be let into the treasure house -- or he will destroy San Lorenzo.

9.title: Sphere

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

9.plot: The Mole King's treasure is missing, and he won't give it up unless Puss helps him get his ex-girlfriend back.

10.title: Si

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

10.plot: Puss fights the Duchess for an object that can help him bring back the magic spell that protects the town.

11.title: No

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

1.title: Bootless Cries

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

3.plot: Puss seeks out his old mentor El Guante Blanco for help defending San Lorenzo, but his mentor has a protégé. Can Puss swallow his pride and not complain.

1.title: Familiar Feeling

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

2.plot: When Puss asks the second witch sister Malaranea for her gem, she casts a spell that makes him a prisoner in his dreams and only Dulcinea can save him.

6.plot: When Dulcinea sets up a school to teach unruly thieves how to be good, Uli takes the idea too far and it's up to Puss to make San Lorenzo normal.

7.plot: When Puss, Dulcinea, and Uli search for a book filled with secrets about the Crown of Souls, they sneak into a mansion and trick an ogre named Tranche.

8.title: Titan Up

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

8.plot: When the Orphans start rumors that Puss has special powers, Taranis the God of Thunder asks Puss to help defeat the most powerful God of all, Toutatis.

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

9.plot: When Roz the boar comes to San Lorenzo to collect a bounty for capturing Puss, Pajuna tries to keep them separated before an epic fight breaks out.

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

11.plot: When Puss and Dulcinea tracked down the Grotto of Riches, they each have their own plan on how to convince Mary and her flock to help find the Obelisk.

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

12.plot: When time is running out for Puss to find the Obelisk, he must fight El Moco and finds out who The One from the Great Prophecy is.

13.title: The Bloodwolf

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

13.plot: When Puss is dealing with the apparent loss of Dulcinea, the mighty fear-eating Bloodwolf arrives and brings out Puss's greatest fears.

1.title: Second to One

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

1.plot: The Bloodwolf's been defeated, and all seems right in San Lorenzo. Puss, no longer the No. 1 hero and protector, gets restless and tries on a new hat.

2.title: Not a Drill

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

2.plot: The threat of monsters from the Netherworld portal has Puss running the townspeople through some crazy emergency drills, which no one takes seriously.

3.title: Caballo Sin Cabeza

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

3.plot: When a headless horse emerges from the portal seeking the perfect noggin, the San Lorenzans try to deter the creature without losing one of their own.

5.plot: Our furry hero is amused at first when the portal coughs up a bunch of Puss clones, each with a unique personality. But then he meets his evil twin.

7.title: The Iceman Melteth

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

7.plot: A vengeful ice monster who attacks Puss starts melting, so Puss and Artephius conjure ways to keep him cool while Dulcinea works on his bucket list.

8.plot: Toby falls in with a pack of ill-intentioned imps determined to wreak havoc on Lord Crispintine's Day, the holiday when San Lorenzans celebrate love.

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

9.plot: A putrid stench in San Lorenzo has everyone scrambling to find the source. Eames identifies it right away, but as usual, no one pays attention to him.

10.title: Dances with Dingoes

episode of.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots (TV Series 2015–2018)

10.plot: A charming dingo teaches the villagers a new dance, much to Flamenco-loving Puss's chagrin. But Dulcinea becomes suspicious of her hypnotic gyrations.

imdb.plot outline: A spectacular C"G action-comedy, THE ADVENTURES OF PUSS IN BOOTS stars one of DreamWorks Animation's most celebrated characters. The world's greatest fighter, lover (and milk connoisseur) springs to action with mystical, comical tales that take him to exotic locations filled with unforgettable characters.
imdb.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots
plot: The famous cat protects the city of San Lorenzo, a mythical land invisible to the outside world.::Jwelch5742

A spectacular C"G action-comedy, THE ADVENTURES OF PUSS IN BOOTS stars one of DreamWorks Animation's most celebrated characters. The world's greatest fighter, lover (and milk connoisseur) springs to action with mystical, comical tales that take him to exotic locations filled with unforgettable characters.
